{"tid":642067,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老公殺妻拎頭顱周街行 街坊懵然不知","createTime":"2018-04-25T12:59:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-25T13:08:38.000Z","uid":157545,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"17a9ee778d8c03415fcae2d92f63903d929011ff","tid":642067,"uid":157545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T12:59:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180425/large/1524655550_911f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180425%2Flarge%2F1524655550_911f.jpg&h=c120fc2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n廣州海珠區康樂村發生駭人兇殺案。一名張姓男子殺死妻子後，竟割下其頭顱，隨後更大搖大擺走上街頭。警方今日通報案情，兇手於今晨自首。經初步審查，張男指因家庭糾紛殺死其夏姓妻子。目前，該案正在進一步偵辦中。<br />\n<br />\n而網上更流傳一段有指是兇手拿着一個頭顱的物體走上街。當時身邊的民眾都未有查覺。繼續如常走路。"},{"pid":"5513c670a8e0d1f46116fd1e0ed0eab01f80d4e3","tid":642067,"uid":163350,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T13:02:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0c4f03fad9ce0cfaf8b18a3683271c1405744de0","tid":642067,"uid":59567,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T13:02:18.000Z","msg":"係鬼國有乜出奇"},{"pid":"5a2f891138193a4cabe337921ab66a6a5bc386c8","tid":642067,"uid":82532,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T13:05:18.000Z","msg":"喺香港個個dup低頭玩手機都未必有人知啦"},{"pid":"ea31429e3493aa6d0f6091f6112f16ddb4670582","tid":642067,"uid":86841,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T13:08:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5a7d2efa619ef12187fa4ae602b3231a240063ae","tid":642067,"uid":56240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T13:08:38.000Z","msg":"想睇"}]}